			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><span style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;">Ravindra degree college is a part of ravindra educational institutions which was established in the year 1985. it is a pioneer institute imparting the knowledge in the areas of lifesciences and commerce.</span><br style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;">         ravindra institutions under the dynamic leadership of honarable secretary g.pullaiah garu , madam principal mamatha garu , has been strengthening college developement activities to bring fruits of research for betterment of society with the able support and vauble guidance of a the faculity.</span><br style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;">           the college offers 5 b ranches in the UG level. the college has excelent infrastructural facilities including modern laboratories, library and also good hostal facility . the college also provides a facility of scholarship to the students.</span></p></div>]]></description>
